About ByteDance:
Founded in 2012, ByteDance's mission is to inspire creativity and enrich life. With a suite of more than a dozen products, including TikTok, Helo & Resso, as well as platforms specific to the Chinese market including Douyin, Toutiao & Xigua, ByteDance has made it easier and more fun for people to connect with, consume & create content.

About the team:
Finance investment team is the capital investment arm of ByteDance, that makes financially driven investments in broad range of fields covering Internet, software, and hardware to clean-tech, health care and consumer. Now the team expands its exploration worldwide and seeks to discover high-value companies in different stages.

Responsibilities:

Participate in investment market research and investment strategy creation of US;
Maintain relationships with investors and founders in US, hold necessary meetings and activities, identify industry trends and investment opportunities;
Work closely with teammates across countries; lead deal sourcing, investment discussion and deal execution including due diligence, financial modeling and transaction negotiations;
Build relationships with internal cross-functional teams including finance and legal functions and related business teams
In charge of portfolio management, including post deal review, risk alert, value creation, exit and etc..

Qualifications:

5+ years experience in venture capital in the technology industry;
Deal execution, negotiation and exit experience;
Demonstrated experience influencing and communicating effectively across countries and organization;
Demonstrated analytical skills, including industry and technology research, quantitative analysis, financial modeling;
Demonstrated understanding of the technology industry, including semiconductor, cloud computing, AI, SaaS and so on, experts in biotech is a plus;
Strong curiosity and self-driven, multi-task management skills, continuous learner.

ByteDance is committed to creating an inclusive space where employees are valued for their skills, experiences, and unique perspectives. Our products connect people from across the globe and so does our workplace. At Bytedance, our mission is to inspire creativity and enrich life. To achieve that goal, we are committed to celebrating our diverse voices and to creating an environment that reflects the many communities we reach. We believe individuals shouldn't be disadvantaged because of their background or identity, but instead should be considered based on their strengths and experience.

ByteDance is committed to providing reasonable accommodations during our recruitment process. If you need assistance or an accommodation, please reach out to us at USRC@bytedance.com

